Package: biomartr
Title: Genomic Data Retrieval with R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Hajk-Georg Drost
Maintainer: Hajk-Georg Drost <hgd23@cam.ac.uk>
Description: Perform genomic data retrieval and functional annotation with
    R. This tool provides API functions to the 'BioMart' database and genome retrieval
    functions for bulk retrieval of genomes.
VignetteBuilder: knitr
NeedsCompilation: yes
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.1)
Imports:
    biomaRt,
    Biostrings,
    data.table (>= 1.9.4),
    dplyr (>= 0.3.0),
    readr (>= 0.2.2),
    downloader (>= 0.3),
    RCurl (>= 1.95-4.5),
    XML (>= 3.98-1.1),
    httr (>= 0.6.1),
    stringr (>= 0.6.2)
Suggests:
    knitr (>= 1.6),
    rmarkdown (>= 0.3.3),
    devtools (>= 1.6.1),
    testthat
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/HajkD/biomartr
BugReports: https://github.com/HajkD/biomartr/issues
